lass=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉"},{"pid":"10abfa6e020c965d049f5e0381acfae582346b98","tid":1808151,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:53:37.000Z","msg":"弱智？"},{"pid":"b72805c34c909199ad63ed457ce2f2869c024b4a","tid":1808151,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c6ab253f074c71df04a64cd4898296a72d9b7e40","tid":1808151,"uid":18484,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:51:08.000Z","msg":"一個將軍澳 一個屯門啊 大哥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:53:46.000Z","msg":"樓主 弱智 confirmed <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43b637eec6e9ad0cb32aa5a30d3fccb03736e60","tid":1808151,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:54:30.000Z","msg":"屌你reading 0分咪撚搞咁撚多野啦<br />\n睇下po咪算"},{"pid":"36006e853328b54189cdf2ccd65de94895c714b9","tid":1808151,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ndse 中文2都拎唔到就係你依種人?"},{"pid":"a1293ce4cc2262d6e598e2e1810c7f98b634b9b9","tid":1808151,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:54:34.000Z","msg":"樓主睇錯唔好推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712c7951fb9c709d3b8d3981a5fc495c1688c4d9","tid":1808151,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:55:19.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"4b6f70defea2b3a480bde602d4342df3442f0a3b","tid":1808151,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"咁都有得笑"},{"pid":"f845237dcfe459f1367ea407c1d677cf414743e4","tid":1808151,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vety0xq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvety0xq.png&h=c803897e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解2003年沙士香港有299人死亡？而新加坡得33人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為當年個仆街政府草菅人命，冇一早隔離大陸病人呀！<br />\n<br />\n咁你信唔信依家呢個政府會話俾你知真相？佢咁驚經濟差，仲會提你帶口罩？佢就係唔想人人帶口罩呀！<br />\n<br />\n有兩單病情穩定案例？好，咁你諗吓，假設你喺大陸中咗招，知道喺大陸好大機會死，而死咗官方都唔會認，咁你又知道香港醫生好犀利，咁你會點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾我就會先搭車去深圳，再落嚟香港，咁你個海關唔通每個大陸人都檢疫咩？<br />\n<br />\n為求自保，出街帶口罩啦<br />\n<br />\n要一人行一步，防止社區爆發呀</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XFrgXW1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXFrgXW1.png&h=6510022b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZajN290.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZajN290.png&h=23786f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZaEUdw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZaEUdw.png&h=9c751baa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEvJBhZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEvJBhZ.png&h=95690e68&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X59uwRt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX59uwRt.png&h=40f9ad0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08TZUer.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08TZUer.png&h=dc5f3de9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/